---
title: Summer BBQ Chicken Plates with Maple Bacon Beans & Charred Corn Salad
description: These plates are packed with summery flavors. First, you’ll char sweet corn, then mix the kernels into a spoonable salad with tomato, scallion, and a creamy dressing. Next up, you’ll simmer beans with bacon, maple syrup, and a slew of smoky spices. The main event: BBQ chicken, basted with a rich sauce and topped with zingy pickled onions. Whether you serve this dinner plated or buffet style, get ready for an effortless backyard (or indoor!) BBQ.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/summer-bbq-chicken-plates-3a9ac91a.jpg
